Royal Bank of Canada &lt;RT.TO>  said itis extending its discount brokerage service which has beenavailable to Ontario residents since last year, to Quebecinvestors.    The bank said the success of the Ontario service is alsoprompting it to consider making the service available inseveral other provinces.    Royal Bank said the service offers cuts of up to 75 pct onstandard brokerage commissions, toll-free, up-to-the-minutestock quotes, and margin loans in U.S. or Canadian dollars atcompetitive rates. Reuter&#3;